# Note: crates/server/resources/settings.yaml is the committed dev-default
# (referenced via embed_data in crates/server/BUILD.bazel as the only file
# the public OSS build needs). Do NOT gitignore it: the umbrella's OSS
# sync drops gitignored files from the NVIDIA/nvcf mirror, breaking the
# GHA Bazel matrix with `glob pattern 'resources/*.yaml' didn't match`.
